data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: In the picture, a large hot-air balloon tilts, and two guys are trying to get the passager off the balloon. I am not sure whether it is a successful landing, but I always feel like it's so dangerous to take a hot-air balloon. There are thousands of hot-air balloon accidents reported every year,  and among the most common are such issues as running into power wires or having an unusually hard landing. Sometimes weather, such as lightning, is the cause of hot air balloon accidents, and errors made by the pilot, helpers, or passengers can cause issues as well. So for me, I would never try something like that in the picture.
